eloper Productivity (IA Generativa)</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">I</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;"><strong>R</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">A</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">I</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">C</td></tr><tr style="background:#ffffff;"><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">Piloto AIOps / Observability inteligente</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">I</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;"><strong>R</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">C</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">I</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">C</td></tr><tr style="background:#faf5ff;"><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">MLOps básico (CI/CD para modelos)</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">I</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;"><strong>R</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">A</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">I</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">I</td></tr><tr style="background:#ffffff;"><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">Capacitação Wave 1 e Wave 2</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">A</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">C</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;"><strong>R</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">I</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;"><strong>A</strong></td></tr><tr style="background:#faf5ff;"><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">AI Value Framework e dashboard de ROI</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">I</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">C</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">A</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;"><strong>R</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">C</td></tr><tr style="background:#ffffff;"><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">Plataforma centralizada de IA (escala)</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">I</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;"><strong>R</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;"><strong>A</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">C</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">C</td></tr><tr style="background:#faf5ff;"><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">Mapeamento de casos de uso por BU</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">C</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">C</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;"><strong>R</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">A</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;"><strong>A</strong></td></tr><tr style="background:#ffffff;"><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">Programa AI Champions e comunidade de prática</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;"><strong>A</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">I</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;"><strong>R</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">I</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">C</td></tr><tr style="background:#faf5ff;"><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">Monitoramento contínuo e SLAs de modelos</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">I</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;"><strong>R</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">A</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">I</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">C</td></tr><tr style="background:#ffffff;"><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">Estruturação de oferta AIaaS para clientes</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;"><strong>A</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">C</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;"><strong>R</strong></td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">C</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">C</td></tr><tr style="background:#faf5ff;"><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">IA Agêntica em processos internos</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;">I</td><td style="border:1px solid #e9d5ff;padding:7pt 10pt;vertical-align:top;"><strong>R</strong></td>